This is the template to provision Windows server using Ansible.
====================

Steps:

1. Add your own AWS credentials into vars/aws-creds.yml
2. Edit vars/environment.yml to define the security groups, sets of instances, etc
3. Make sure boto and boto3 have been installed on Ansible machine
`sudo pip install boto`  
`sudo pip install boto3`  
4. Make sure the RDP SG doesn't exist in AWS.
5. Run: ansible-playbook -i hosts provision.yml

